name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: PR to Master Warning for GitHub

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Ask for confirmation when creating a PR to master branch on GitHub

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If your team has git workflow restricts creating PRs to master, which is a default target, you may find this extension helpful.

By default, it will make a confirmation dialog to appear whenever you attempt to create a PR targeted to master. You can whitelist organizations and usernames in the extension options to limit where the confirmation will appear. 

Icon is composed from openclipart.org assets attributed to _o and jhnri4.
